  "title": "CONSTRUCTION REBAR WORKER",
  "description": "<p>1.Accurately measuring, cutting, and assembling Rebar<br /></p><p>2.Reading and interpreting blueprints, sketches, and technical specifications to ensure accurate construction.<br /></p><p>3.Operating power tools, hand tools and measurement tools (powered saws, hammers, rulers etc.)<br /></p><p>4.Cut, shape timber according to measurements/requirements<br /></p><p>5.Maintaining a clean and organised worksite to promote safety and efficiency<br /></p><p>6.Completing all work to a high standard of quality and within agreed timelines<br /></p><p>Requirements:<br /></p><p>1.Relevant 2 years experience in Rebar<br /></p><p>2.Good physical condition to carry out hands-on work<br /></p><p>3.Ability to read technical drawings and handle tools safely<br /></p><p>4.Positive attitude and team player</p>",
